{
  "stem": "5559.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they published that picture, and they show us slaughterhouse-- about 12 Jews with their feet up, with their heads down hanging, and their skin was taken off, and it says in Romanian, [SPEAKING ROMANIAN].",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[?Karne?] in romanian means meat, kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you didn't need much report, you had it from Germany or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was right there, right in front of your nose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember that the Betar, where I belong under the Revisionists, tried to organize the youngsters and tell them, they want to take us Aliyah Bet-- that is the illegal, you know, immigration.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the English cut up them with you and put you on Cyprus, everybody heard about.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They want to take Aliyah Bet the youngsters, to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, I was the only son.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And God bless my aunt-- I should remember now, my aunt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had an aunt in New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew, we call her, tante, which is aunt, Mindell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was her first name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her last name was Goodman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she-- she stay in the front a tall, [INAUDIBLE], very nice woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she came and she was staying then with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I love my tante, because she was very sweet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I confessed in her that one day I will join the Betar, and run away from home and go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My tante felt her duty, she had to tell that to my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm the only son and I want to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I bring it just up, because it was ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They knew what's going on, at least to save somebody, go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, I never forget that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the only time when I be very severe punished by my father, may he rest in peace.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
